    "en": {
      "title": "What happened to Asia's largest ruby?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Asia's largest ruby \u200b\u200bfound in Sri Lanka was taken to Switzerland six months ago but has not yet been sold, said Thilak Weerasinghe, chairman of the Gem and Jewelery Authority.",
        "Sources in the authority said that the 530 kg ruby \u200b\u200bwas taken without the 25% deposit required for export. But only the thousand rupees required to take the gem for examination has been paid to the official. (R)"
      ],
